  <Title>Medenia Spirit Worship</Title>
  <Type>1</Type>
  <Content>On Tuesday, July 17th, the Medenia Spirit Worship will be released. Only the Earth and Fire Spirits will be available for this release.  Medenia path Aislings can become worshipers of a Medenia Spirit by gaining levels of reverence. Each level of reverence will allow an Aisling to perform different levels of mass, granting Aislings with a spirit specific item.


Reverence 1
Ability Mass -grants the group performing this mass ability points.

Reverence 2
Ability Mass - more points than reverence 1.
Earring Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit earring. (Earth Spirit Earring).

Reverence 3
