Ability Mass - more points than reverence 2.
Earring Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit earring. (Earth Spirit Earring).
Ring Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit ring.


Reverence 4
Ability Mass - more points than reverence 3.
Earring Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit earring. (Earth Spirit Earring).
Ring Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit ring.
Necklace Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit necklace.

Reverence 5
Ability Mass - more points than reverence 4.
Earring Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit earring. (Earth Spirit Earring).
Ring Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit ring.
Necklace Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit necklace.
Pet Mass - grants the group performing this mass a spirit pet.

Gaining reverence and performing mass is done be reciting set lines.  Each reverence level will have a different set of lines.

Example:
"Oh good Earth, oh great Earth."
"I thank you for your nurturing soil and essential ores."
"It is so."</Content>
